AB  - The statistical properties of the maximum likelihood estimator (M.L.E.) of the parameters of a linear model with Gamma distributed residuals are analysed. Some previous results of the literature on this topic are corrected, allowing the computation of the asymptotic relative efficiency of the M.L.E. over the O.L.S.
